{"tid":1470620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實可唔可以唔好再舉英國旗？","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:50:13.000Z","uid":5822,"like":13,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a195716ebff8424c36b77eed454b46488918b932","tid":1470620,"uid":5822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"你地爭取外國注意我明<br />\n但英國管香港時 華人同狗係一樣等級 <br />\n可唔可以唔好再吹奏英國呢個垃圾國家？<br />\n可唔可以理解下英國管治香港既歷史？<br />\n<br />\n其實英國管香港時都係極權統治者黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係撞正經濟起飛先無咩人反 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">英國絕對係一個最虛偽既國家 滿口道德人義 但係非我族類 其心必異 </span>"},{"pid":"b783a2adece2bd06f0acf073751a1cadd55a2f24","tid":1470620,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"統一戰線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45fd9803399b181f113ae469e00fe8ea114b5b49","tid":1470620,"uid":5822,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b783a2adece2bd06f0acf073751a1cadd55a2f24","tid":1470620,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"統一戰線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:12:03.000Z","msg":"英國統治比中共統治更為霸道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d